title: Eight Immortals - Jurong East
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Fast food, Take-out, Singaporean
description: Food stall at the Kopi food court on the ground floor of Jurong East MRT station. Big buffet portions with soup. Has brown rice, economy rice, nasi briyani, nasi lemak, tom yam bee hoon soup, dumpling noodles, crispy noodles, laksa, fried rice, lontong, lor mee and sliced fish porridge. Uses dairy in curries - ask.
